name: PharmWeb3 Token
description: PharmWeb3 is a cutting-edge platform that combines healthcare access with Web3 technology. By performing tasks, engaging with the community, or referring friends, you earn $PW3 tokens, which can be used for trade, discounts, or to get free medical products and services. Our goal is to lower healthcare barriers globally by leveraging blockchain rewards and decentralization. We partner with pharmacies, clinics, and healthcare providers to ensure users benefit from real-world medical assistance, while focusing on security and trust to build a committed community. Whether you're here to earn tokens, request free drugs, or explore the future of healthcare technology, welcome to the PharmWeb3 family. Together, we can redefine healthcare on a global scale.
